divs: Sighting DetailsEveryone said they heard a boom and that their homes had shook. I called 911 and they had no information. I also called the local t.v. news station and the woman at the news desk ,told me that I was the first person to call and that she had heard something, but she thought it had been their heating.
Summary: Never saw anything , but a loud boom shook the entire house. I went outside to find that several of our neighbors had also gone outside.
